 Pepper Stew | Photo Kourtney Jackson Eid is here again and you are going to be left with pieces of ram meat to do as you please. One of the best methods to use for your ram during Eid is to prepare pepper stew which is called Omi Obe in Yoruba part of Nigeria. This stew can be served with any swallow of your choice. Ingredients Pepper Stew | Photo Alex Williams Method